OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFormer Israeli PMs         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FNetanyahu and Olmert face  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Foff in court in libel case 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Two former Israeli prime ministers have
OL,6, faced off in court in Tel Aviv, as     
OL,7, Benjamin Netanyahu and his family began
OL,8, a defamation suit against Ehud Olmert. 
OL,10,FMr Netanyahu, his wife Sara, and their 
OL,11,Feldest son Yair are suing Mr Olmert for
OL,12,F$269,000 (#198,000) in damages for     
OL,13,Fsaying that they were mentally ill.    
OL,15,FMr Olmert made the claim in two Israeli
OL,16,FTV interviews last April.              
OL,18,FHe is arguing that it was not libellous
OL,19,Fbecause it was true, and also that he  
OL,20,Fwas clearly expressing an opinion.     
